article.description: — Dimencio Vaughn had 24 points and Allen Powell scored 18 as Rider topped Siena 74-60 on Friday night.
article.headline: Vaughn scores 24 to lead Rider past Siena 74-60
article.linkText: Vaughn scores 24 to lead Rider past Siena 74-60
article.story: ALBANY, N.Y. -- — Dimencio Vaughn had 24 points and Allen Powell scored 18 as Rider topped Siena 74-60 on Friday night. Ajiri Ogemuno-Johnson added 10 points and nine rebounds for Rider (8-13, 4-7 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Colby Rogers had 20 points for the Saints (9-9, 6-4). Javian McCollum added 12 points. Aidan Carpenter had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
